row.InputSentence1: Maureen has always wanted to become a Biology teacher.
row.InputSentence2: She studies very hard to become an expert in Biology.
row.InputSentence3: Her friends tell her that Biology is too tough for her.
row.InputSentence4: However, she continues until she has her degree.
row.RandomFifthSentenceQuiz1: Maureen said girls didn't belong in science professions.
row.RandomFifthSentenceQuiz2: Now Maureen shares her passion for Biology with students.
